"17:13:2" : {s: 17, a: 13, w: 2, r: "انس", t: "إِنسَٰنٍ", l: "إِنسَٰن", lc: 71, tl: "insānin", lb: "মানুষ",e: "man", b: "মানুষ", i: "manusia", f: 1, rm: "to be or become sociable, companionable, conversable, inclined to company or conversation, friendly, amicable, or familiar. To be or become cheered, or gladdened or cheerful, gay, or gladsome. To be or become at ease, or tranquil; without shrinking or aversion."},
